name: Euphoric
description:
#2
In the afternoon around 04.00 pm, I look at the river
something attract me to see and capture,
a father carrying her daughter to take a bath in the river flow
such a beauty seeing, one thing that reminds me now is,
I have a beatiful daughter, about 1 year old now, always sobbing begged me to hold her and carrying her, and then she just lending her head in my arm, suddenly her teardrop just dissapear.
Maybe there's some point when old man saying, 
a daughter first love is her father .
